01:08:33,160 --> 01:08:37,170
No, of course not. She's a lady.
No, she's not that either.

763
01:08:50,220 --> 01:08:54,190
Darlin'. Never let the sun
Go down on an argument,

764
01:08:54,190 --> 01:08:58,190
As jody used to say.
What are you doing here ?

765
01:08:58,630 --> 01:08:59,930
Got your note.

766
01:08:59,930 --> 01:09:02,700
So let's kiss and make up, honey.
Don't call me that.

767
01:09:02,700 --> 01:09:04,730
Sorry, darling.
Stop it, dil.

768
01:09:04,730 --> 01:09:06,970
Apologies, my sweet.

769
01:09:09,540 --> 01:09:13,540
That's more like it, dear.
Have a cuppa.

770
01:09:19,420 --> 01:09:22,320
You're somethin' else, dil.
You know that ?

771
01:09:22,320 --> 01:09:24,620
Never said a truer word.

772
01:09:24,620 --> 01:09:26,890
I was always best
Lookin' after someone.

773
01:09:26,890 --> 01:09:30,560
- must be something
In the genes.
- must be.

774
01:09:30,560 --> 01:09:32,800
And the fact that
You didn't know...

775
01:09:32,800 --> 01:09:34,370
Is basically the fault
Of yours truly.

776
01:09:34,370 --> 01:09:38,370
And even when
You were throwin' up,
I could tell you cared.

777
01:09:39,140 --> 01:09:43,140
- you could ?
- do you care, jimmy ?

778
01:09:43,680 --> 01:09:46,450
Yeah. Sure I do.

779
01:09:46,450 --> 01:09:49,650
You mean that ?
Yeah.

780
01:09:49,650 --> 01:09:51,420
I care, dil.

781
01:09:54,160 --> 01:09:58,160
Are you crying ?

782
01:10:04,400 --> 01:10:07,800
I'm tired and emotional.

783
01:10:07,800 --> 01:10:11,610
Do it on your own time, pat.
What ?

784
01:10:11,610 --> 01:10:13,510
Whatever it is
She does for you.

785
01:10:13,510 --> 01:10:15,210
If I was her,
I'd consider that
An insult.

786
01:10:15,210 --> 01:10:19,220
Consider it how you like.
Just get the bloody tart
Out of here !

787
01:10:22,190 --> 01:10:25,990
Didja ever
Pick your teeth up
With broken fingers ?

788
01:10:25,990 --> 01:10:28,830
What's that
Supposed to mean ?

789
01:10:28,830 --> 01:10:32,830
A simple question.

790
01:10:35,830 --> 01:10:39,840
- come on, dear.
- he didn't answer, honey.

791
01:10:41,480 --> 01:10:45,080
Sorry about that, mr. Deveroux.

792
01:10:45,080 --> 01:10:47,920
My, oh my, jimmy, how gallant.
Shut up.

793
01:10:47,920 --> 01:10:51,250
Made me feel all funny inside.
I said stop it.

794
01:10:51,250 --> 01:10:53,850
Ask to meet me again,
Jimmy.

795
01:10:53,850 --> 01:10:57,830
Do you think that's wise ?
Nothing's wise.

796
01:10:57,830 --> 01:11:01,830
 I didn't mean to hit you.
I know that.

797
01:11:02,400 --> 01:11:06,240
I kinda liked you as a girl.
That's a start.

798
01:11:06,240 --> 01:11:09,710
So, I'm sorry.
So, make it up to me,
Then.

799
01:11:09,710 --> 01:11:13,710
How ?
Ask to meet me again.

800
01:11:14,580 --> 01:11:18,580
Will you meet me again ?
When ?

801
01:11:18,680 --> 01:11:21,350
Whenever.

802
01:11:21,350 --> 01:11:24,160
Tonight.

803
01:11:35,940 --> 01:11:39,940
Good night.
See ya later.

804
01:11:40,510 --> 01:11:42,280
Do they know ?
Know what, honey ?

805
01:11:42,280 --> 01:11:46,050
Know what I didn't know. And don't call me that.
Can't help it.

806
01:11:46,050 --> 01:11:49,450
A girl has her feelings.
Thing is, dil,
You're not a girl.

807
01:11:49,450 --> 01:11:53,460
Details, baby, details.
So they do know.

808
01:11:53,790 --> 01:11:55,990
All right, they do.
Don't.

809
01:11:55,990 --> 01:12:00,000
 I shoulda known,
Shouldn't I ?
Probably.

810
01:12:00,760 --> 01:12:04,770
Kinda wish I didn't.
You can always pretend.

811
01:12:04,970 --> 01:12:08,310
Ah, that's true.

812
01:12:08,310 --> 01:12:10,670
Your soldier knew,
Didn't he ?

813
01:12:10,670 --> 01:12:12,510
Absolutely.

814
01:12:12,510 --> 01:12:16,510
Won't be quite the same, though, will it ?
Are you pretendin' yet ?

815
01:12:18,150 --> 01:12:22,150
I'm workin' on it.

816
01:12:22,920 --> 01:12:24,790
There's dave.

817
01:12:24,790 --> 01:12:27,690
He knew too.
Stop it, jimmy.

818
01:12:27,690 --> 01:12:31,200
Am I becoming
Repetitious ?

819
01:12:31,200 --> 01:12:34,500
A little. Sorry.

820
01:12:34,500 --> 01:12:38,010
No, don't ask me in.
Please, jimmy.

821
01:12:38,010 --> 01:12:42,010
No.
Can't pretend that much.

822
01:12:42,480 --> 01:12:45,080
I miss you, jimmy.
Yeah ?

823
01:12:45,080 --> 01:12:49,080
Shoulda stayed a girl.
Don't be cruel.

824
01:12:51,420 --> 01:12:53,960
Okay.

825
01:12:53,960 --> 01:12:57,860
Be a good girl.
Go inside.

826
01:12:57,860 --> 01:13:01,870
Only if you kiss me.

827
01:13:11,240 --> 01:13:15,250
Now are you happy ?
Delirious.

828
01:13:27,490 --> 01:13:31,230
Hello, stranger.

829
01:13:31,230 --> 01:13:34,270
You vanished.

830
01:13:34,270 --> 01:13:37,270
What was it, fergus ?
Did you blow the gaff
On us...

831
01:13:37,270 --> 01:13:40,970
Or did you just
Fuck up ?

832
01:13:40,970 --> 01:13:43,180
Leave me alone, jude.

833
01:13:43,180 --> 01:13:47,180
No. That's the last thing
I'll do.

834
01:13:55,120 --> 01:13:58,600
- you never asked
What happened.
- I heard.

835
01:13:58,600 --> 01:14:01,330
Eddie and tinker died.
I know.

836
01:14:01,330 --> 01:14:05,340
Maguire and me got out
By the skin of our teeth,
No thanks to you.

837
01:14:08,810 --> 01:14:11,840
What do you think
Of my hair ?

838
01:14:11,840 --> 01:14:14,310
Suits you. Aye.

839
01:14:14,310 --> 01:14:17,720
I was sick of bein'
A blond.

840
01:14:17,720 --> 01:14:21,720
I needed a tougher look,
If you know what I mean.

841
01:14:32,700 --> 01:14:36,700
Fuck me, fergus.

842
01:14:37,440 --> 01:14:41,440
Am I to take it
That's a no ?

843
01:14:42,810 --> 01:14:46,050
We had a court-martial
In your absence.

844
01:14:46,050 --> 01:14:48,720
They wanted to
Put a bullet
Through your head.

845
01:14:48,720 --> 01:14:50,550
I pleaded for clemency.

846
01:14:50,550 --> 01:14:54,560
Said we should find out
What happened first.

847
01:14:55,260 --> 01:14:58,560
So what did happen ?

848
01:14:58,560 --> 01:15:00,100
He ran.

849
01:15:00,100 --> 01:15:03,300
I couldn't shoot him
In the back.

850
01:15:03,300 --> 01:15:05,740
Tried to catch him.

851
01:15:05,740 --> 01:15:09,740
He made it to the road
And got hit by a saracen.

852
01:15:10,340 --> 01:15:14,350
So you did fuck up.
Yes.

853
01:15:14,450 --> 01:15:18,180
But you know what
The thing is, fergus ?

854
01:15:18,180 --> 01:15:20,190
No. What is the thing ?

855
01:15:20,190 --> 01:15:24,060
You vanished
Quite effectively.

856
01:15:24,060 --> 01:15:25,930
Became mister nobody.

857
01:15:25,930 --> 01:15:28,890
You've no idea
How useful that could be.

858
01:15:28,890 --> 01:15:32,400
What do you mean ?
We've got some plans
Here...

859
01:15:32,400 --> 01:15:36,400
And we'll need
A mister nobody
To execute them.

860
01:15:36,510 --> 01:15:38,910
No way, jude. I'm out.

861
01:15:38,910 --> 01:15:42,910
You're never out,
Fergus.

862
01:15:43,250 --> 01:15:46,950
Maybe you don't care
About yourself, but-

863
01:15:46,950 --> 01:15:50,950
Consider the girl, fergus.

864
01:15:51,690 --> 01:15:52,560
The wee black chick.

865
01:15:52,560 --> 01:15:56,560
- leave her out of this !
- jesus, fergus !
You're a walkin' cliche.

866
01:15:57,730 --> 01:16:01,370
You know we won't
Leave her out of it.

867
01:16:01,370 --> 01:16:05,370
But I'm glad to see
You care.

868
01:16:05,370 --> 01:16:07,410
And, I must admit...

869
01:16:07,410 --> 01:16:10,780
- I'm curious.
- what the fuck
Do you know, jude ?

870
01:16:10,780 --> 01:16:14,610
You fuckin' tell me, boy !

871
01:16:14,610 --> 01:16:18,150
She's nobody.
She likes me.

872
01:16:18,150 --> 01:16:22,150
Oh, so I suppose a fuck
Is out of the question.

873
01:16:23,220 --> 01:16:26,890
You keep your head down,
Fergus.

874
01:16:26,890 --> 01:16:28,960
No sudden moves.

875
01:16:28,960 --> 01:16:32,070
And not a whisper
To her.

876
01:16:32,070 --> 01:16:36,070
You'll be hearin'
From us.

877
01:16:38,410 --> 01:16:42,410
Keep the faith.

878
01:16:59,860 --> 01:17:03,870
He your boyfriend ?

879
01:17:05,840 --> 01:17:09,840
Lucky you.

880
01:17:10,580 --> 01:17:13,150
Carnations.

881
01:17:13,150 --> 01:17:15,850
What ?
He'd bring me
Carnations.

882
01:17:15,850 --> 01:17:19,850
Oh, so I got it wrong, huh ?
Not at all, honey.

883
01:17:19,850 --> 01:17:23,860
Don't. Okay.

884
01:17:27,760 --> 01:17:30,630
Come on. Come on.
Why, honey ?

885
01:17:30,630 --> 01:17:34,640
Gonna tell me why ?
No.

886
01:17:36,140 --> 01:17:40,140
What's wrong, jimmy? You gonna tell me what's wrong ?
No. Not here.

887
01:17:52,460 --> 01:17:54,220
You gonna tell me
What it is ?

888
01:17:54,220 --> 01:17:57,530
Ah. What is it ?
You know her,
Jimmy ?

889
01:17:57,530 --> 01:18:00,400
Jimmy, is it ?
You know me, jimmy ?

890
01:18:00,400 --> 01:18:03,230
- dil, this is jude.
- you following me ?

891
01:18:03,230 --> 01:18:04,900
Yeah ! Just checkin'.

892
01:18:04,900 --> 01:18:08,910
Has he been nice to you, dil ?
Ever so nice.
Aren't you, jimmy ?

893
01:18:09,910 --> 01:18:13,210
That's good. I'm glad.

894
01:18:13,210 --> 01:18:17,220
- young love, as they say.
- absolutely.
The younger the better.

895
01:18:17,820 --> 01:18:21,820
- doesn't come much your way,
I suppose.
- don't go lookin' for it, dil.

896
01:18:22,520 --> 01:18:25,360
Well, maybe you'll
Get lucky someday.

897
01:18:25,360 --> 01:18:27,760
Bit heavy on the powder,
Isn't she, jimmy ?

898
01:18:27,760 --> 01:18:31,770
- a girl has to have
A bit of glamour.
- oh, absolutely.

899
01:18:32,700 --> 01:18:35,500
As long
As she can keep it.

900
01:18:35,500 --> 01:18:39,510
Isn't that right, james ?

901
01:18:46,880 --> 01:18:50,250
It's her, isn't it ?
What's her ?

902
01:18:50,250 --> 01:18:53,960
She's the thing
You had to tell me.

903
01:18:53,960 --> 01:18:55,660
Kind of.

904
01:18:55,660 --> 01:18:59,670
I'm sorry, you know that ?
I'm really sorry.

905
01:19:01,670 --> 01:19:04,940
- you see that, col ?
- saw it, dil.

906
01:19:04,940 --> 01:19:08,040
- "fuck it" is what I say.
- yeah, fuck it.

907
01:19:08,040 --> 01:19:12,050
- fuckin' men, col.
- fuck 'em.

908
01:19:12,850 --> 01:19:16,850
Fuck you, jimmy !

909
01:19:34,070 --> 01:19:38,080
- you could always
Make it up to her.
- how ?

910
01:19:38,210 --> 01:19:42,210
When a girl runs out
Like that, she generally
Wants to be followed.

911
01:19:42,250 --> 01:19:45,450
She's not a girl, col.

912
01:19:45,450 --> 01:19:49,450
Whatever you say.

913
01:20:01,200 --> 01:20:05,200
She went that way,
But you go with me.

914
01:20:34,470 --> 01:20:37,140
So, it was you
All the time.

915
01:20:37,140 --> 01:20:41,150
Who'd you think it was ?
I thought it was dave.

916
01:20:42,150 --> 01:20:45,220
And who's dave
When he's at home ?

917
01:20:45,220 --> 01:20:47,220
He's at home.

918
01:20:47,220 --> 01:20:51,090
Should blow you away, you know that.
Yeah, I know.

919
01:20:51,090 --> 01:20:52,060
Aah ! Ohh !

920
01:20:52,060 --> 01:20:55,160
I'm gettin' emotional,
And I don't like gettin'
Fuckin' emotional !

921
01:20:55,160 --> 01:20:58,370
You understand, hennessy ?

922
01:20:58,370 --> 01:21:01,070
Yeah. I understand.
Fuck you too.

923
01:21:01,070 --> 01:21:02,770
Fuck you.

924
01:21:02,770 --> 01:21:04,640
Ah, leave him alone, peter.

925
01:21:04,640 --> 01:21:08,640
- he's in love.
- that right, fergus ?
You in love ?

926
01:21:08,710 --> 01:21:11,980
Absolutely.
And what's she like
Between the sheets ?

927
01:21:11,980 --> 01:21:15,720
Definitely unusual.
And who is she ?

928
01:21:15,720 --> 01:21:17,690
Just a girl.

929
01:21:17,690 --> 01:21:21,690
You know what'll happen
If you fuck up again,
Don't ya ?

930
01:21:21,990 --> 01:21:26,000
Yeah, I do, peter.
Good.

931
01:21:37,440 --> 01:21:41,450
So, what do you think that is, hennessy ?
A hotel ?

932
01:21:43,410 --> 01:21:46,950
It's a knockin' shop.
Tres discreet, huh ?

933
01:21:46,950 --> 01:21:50,090
He visits his ladies
Tuesdays and thursday nights...

934
01:21:50,090 --> 01:21:54,090
And saturday mornings.
That's his security
In the car beyond.

935
01:21:57,030 --> 01:22:00,800
- who is he ?
- doesn't matter who he is.
He's a legitimate target.

936
01:22:00,800 --> 01:22:04,800
- thank god for that.
- you tryin' to be cynical,
Hennessy ?

937
01:22:05,370 --> 01:22:08,410
Hope not. Good.

938
01:22:08,410 --> 01:22:12,410
So, what do you think ?

939
01:22:15,450 --> 01:22:19,460
Whoever hits him will be hit,
If those men are any good.

940
01:22:21,090 --> 01:22:24,460
- and I presume
You can't get inside.
- right.

941
01:22:24,460 --> 01:22:28,470
- so it's on the street ?
- right.

942
01:22:28,470 --> 01:22:32,200
Kind of suicide, isn't it ?

943
01:22:32,200 --> 01:22:35,270
But then,
I don't have a choice.

944
01:22:35,270 --> 01:22:38,480
Oh, you do, fergie.

945
01:22:38,480 --> 01:22:41,110
Of course.

946
01:22:41,110 --> 01:22:43,320
I forgot.

947
01:22:43,320 --> 01:22:45,880
Come on.

948
01:22:45,880 --> 01:22:49,890
Rehearsal.

949
01:22:58,830 --> 01:23:01,440
You keep your mind
On your job, boy.

950
01:23:01,440 --> 01:23:05,440
Then you'll leave her out of it ?
Aye. Then we'll
Leave her be.

951
01:23:09,310 --> 01:23:13,320
He's arthritic.
Takes him two minutes
To get to the door.

952
01:23:16,180 --> 01:23:20,190
And what if I say no ?
You know what. Go.

953
01:23:39,580 --> 01:23:43,580
Pardon me, young man !

954
01:23:52,390 --> 01:23:54,430
You were made for this.
Was I ?

955
01:23:54,430 --> 01:23:56,100
Perfect !
What happens then ?

956
01:23:56,100 --> 01:24:00,100
We'll be on the other side. We'll move when you do.
And what if you don't ?

957
01:24:00,770 --> 01:24:04,770
Fergus, I think you don't trust me.
You may be right.

958
01:24:05,540 --> 01:24:09,540
Stay late at your work
Tomorrow night and I'll
Bring you the gear.

959
01:24:11,080 --> 01:24:13,650
Jude. Yes ?

960
01:24:13,650 --> 01:24:17,120
Who is the old geezer ?

961
01:24:17,120 --> 01:24:21,120
Some judge.

962
01:24:32,740 --> 01:24:35,670
Why'd you follow me, dil ?
I was jealous, jimmy.

963
01:24:35,670 --> 01:24:39,680
- you shouldn't be.
- why shouldn't I
Be jealous ?

964
01:24:42,010 --> 01:24:46,020
Don't. My makeup.

965
01:24:51,860 --> 01:24:55,200
She own you, jimmy ?
Yes.

966
01:24:55,200 --> 01:24:59,200
She's from scotland too ?
Yeah, you
Could say that.

967
01:24:59,900 --> 01:25:03,910
And you're not gonna tell me more ?
Can't.

968
01:25:14,020 --> 01:25:18,020
What you doing, jimmy ?

969
01:25:19,220 --> 01:25:23,230
I don't know yet.

970
01:25:23,360 --> 01:25:27,370
Do you like me
Even a little bit ?

971
01:25:30,200 --> 01:25:34,210
More than that.

972
01:25:35,170 --> 01:25:38,940
Come on.
Let's go for a walk.

973
01:25:38,940 --> 01:25:42,950
Do something for me, dil ?
Anything.

974
01:25:43,220 --> 01:25:46,050
You'd do anything
For me ?

975
01:25:46,050 --> 01:25:47,720
I'm afraid so.

976
01:25:47,720 --> 01:25:51,730
You got the keys
To the shop ?

977
01:26:01,740 --> 01:26:05,010
Want another haircut,
Jimmy ?

978
01:26:05,010 --> 01:26:09,010
No.
Come on, sit down.

979
01:26:15,350 --> 01:26:19,360
You'd do anything for me ?
Anything.

980
01:26:21,430 --> 01:26:24,530
No way.
You said anything,
Dil.

981
01:26:24,530 --> 01:26:28,530
A girl has to
Draw the line somewhere.

982
01:26:28,570 --> 01:26:32,570
Want to change you to a man.
Why ?

983
01:26:32,940 --> 01:26:34,940
It's a secret.

984
01:26:34,940 --> 01:26:38,950
Would you like me better that way, jimmy ?
Yes.

985
01:26:39,810 --> 01:26:42,220
And you wouldn't leave me ?
No.

986
01:26:42,220 --> 01:26:46,220
Do you promise ?
I promise.

987
01:26:47,890 --> 01:26:51,890
Go on, then.

988
01:27:11,350 --> 01:27:15,350
You want to make me like him ?
No.

989
01:27:15,420 --> 01:27:18,820
I want to make you
Into something new...

990
01:27:18,820 --> 01:27:22,830
That nobody recognizes.

991
01:27:34,940 --> 01:27:38,950
I don't recognize myself.

992
01:27:40,820 --> 01:27:44,380
No.
Better in the dark.

993
01:27:44,380 --> 01:27:47,690
So it's true, then.
What ?

994
01:27:47,690 --> 01:27:51,690
You like me better like this.
Yes.

995
01:28:02,440 --> 01:28:06,440
No, no. Dil. Dil.
Come on.

996
01:28:07,040 --> 01:28:11,050
Dil.

997
01:28:24,730 --> 01:28:28,730
Turn around.
Turn around.

998
01:28:33,470 --> 01:28:37,480
Baby.

999
01:28:39,980 --> 01:28:41,980
What you doin', honey ?

1000
01:28:41,980 --> 01:28:45,320
Don't call me that.
Sorry.

1001
01:28:45,320 --> 01:28:48,760
What you doin' ?
Try this on.

1002
01:28:48,760 --> 01:28:51,930
